commitMessage:
Chassis links on bmcweb

This commit implements change to publish chassis connectivity for
Chassis on bmcweb if multiple Chassis resource exists in a system.

The chassis connectivity info is fetched from chassis inventory
association in DBus object mapper and published by chassis schema.

Tested:
Build with the entity-manager patch:
https://gerrit.openbmc-project.xyz/c/openbmc/entity-manager/+/44196

Validator has been executed on a real system and no new error has been
found.

